  "texts": [
    "However, on the more challenging datasets such as tweets related to HCR, HPV, and mask wearing, the highest weighted F1-score is only slightly above 0.6, achieved by FLAN-T5-base on the Mask dataset.",
    "The datasets and models also responded differently to further prompt tuning.",
    "Embedding data-specific information into prompts may enhance the performance of zero-shot LLMs, but the benefits depend on the data and contexts.",
    "For example, the Mask dataset benefited the most from data-specific prompts, but the HCR and HPV datasets did not.",
    "FLAN-T5 saw reduced performance when data-specific prompts were used."
  ],
